Class Avenger

java.lang.Object
mru.application.Avenger
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Avenger>
public class Avenger extends Object implements Comparable<Avenger>
This class represents the hero, their alias, name, performer and their frequencies it has setters and getter for the avenger attributes and implements an comparable interface for custom sorting
